Lake St. for 1 block and you will see the garage entrance directly ahead at the intersection of Lower E. Lake and Lower Stetson. Continue driving straight on Lower E. It is located on the south/right-hand side of E Ohio St. (a one-way street) between N State St. and N Wabash Ave. You may also enter this location at its other entrances, 10 E Grand Ave. and 538 N Wabash Ave.

amenities.description: Users may park their own vehicles at this facility.
The facility has a roof over the vehicles.
The surface of the facility is solid, such as asphalt or concrete.
Entering/exiting the facility does not require touching shared surfaces.
The facility has staff on-site for assistance and questions.
